{"tid":1336880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術研究]水馬","createTime":"2019-07-21T06:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T15:06:24.000Z","uid":284817,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab89ff0ee1e0a9ba7957b593d9cf0331a3b7c47d","tid":1336880,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日會出嚟行，但見到咁多水馬，覺得水馬好「亞乍」，想諗方法幫大家破。<br />\n啲水馬用HDPE造（塑膠嘅一種），化學上唔活躍，溶劑難溶。<br />\n所以要用物理方法做，包括鑽、火燒同搭攻城梯。<br />\n唔知鑽有冇得手動、體積小（好似開紅酒咁）？<br />\n火燒就火機啦，或者拜山燒香用嘅火槍都得。<br />\n攻城梯大家可能想像唔到。其實都係搭一個斜台（召集各路搭棚師傅！）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1uuNXr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1uuNXr.png&h=0b6f892d&s={SIZE}\" />，喺唔破壞水馬情況下，等大家可以行去水馬後面。其實唔 定要斜台，只要有4/6個人（兩組或三組人，每組兩個人）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThiSLMv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThiSLMv.png&h=d7b787a6&s={SIZE}\" /> （如圖），右手疊左手，然後左手疊人哋膊頭，就可以以0成本架設人肉攻城梯，概念上就好似呢條片咁<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WeIBh8QYVh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWeIBh8QYVh4&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=79433fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WeIBh8QYVh4</a>。<br />\n<br />\n參考︰<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1332496/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1332496/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最後大家一定要推，畀大家keep住研究，搵到破解方法！"},{"pid":"c9697afbf7d2385d6324075aa9ce7c8a08342009","tid":1336880,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab89ff0ee1e0a9ba7957b593d9cf0331a3b7c47d","tid":1336880,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日會出嚟行，但見到咁多水馬，覺得水馬好「亞乍」，想諗方法幫大家破。<br />\n啲水馬用HDPE造（塑膠嘅一種），化學上唔活躍，溶劑難溶。<br />\n所以要用物理方法做，包括鑽、火燒同搭攻城梯。<br />\n唔知鑽有冇得手動、體積小（好似開